Cease and Desist Authority:

In the event of trademark infringement or activities that violate the terms of this license, the licensor reserves the right, or be pleased, to issue a cease and desist notice. Users must promptly comply with such notices to rectify the infringement.

Rights for Everyone to Obtain a Free Copy of the Code
